title: RuntimeError: ONNX export failed: Couldn't export Python operator GridSampler
body_html:
I tried to use ONNX to transform my Pytorch model but with error like this:

proto = trace.export(list(model.state_dict().values()), _onnx_opset_version)
RuntimeError: ONNX export failed: Couldn't export Python operator GridSampler

It seems ONNX can't find the same method like the Pytorch Function GridSampler. And it was setted UNKNOWN_TYPE on the Layer Operator??? How can I solve it ?

body:
I tried to use ONNX to transform my Pytorch model but with error like this:
```
proto = trace.export(list(model.state_dict().values()), _onnx_opset_version)
RuntimeError: ONNX export failed: Couldn't export Python operator GridSampler
```
It seems ONNX can't find the same method like the Pytorch Function GridSampler. And it was setted `UNKNOWN_TYPE` on the Layer Operator???  How can I solve it ?
